2005-09-18 12:20:56  Rev 7538   josef

	* ggz-kde/src/KGGZ.cpp:
	  - detect aborted game launch when the channel becomes ready
	  In theory, ggzcore would do much more sanity checking on its own.
	  Why this special case happens with Koenig is unclear. It seems that
	  the table launch aborts early, before the channel could be 
	  established,
	  but late enough so that the game is already negotiated.


