	  kio_ggzmeta/kioslave:
	  - Right now I would buy everything which has 'meta server' written 
	  on it, you
	    might think... anyway, here we go:
	  - Imported generic abstraction layer for meta servers of any kind
	  - support for ggzmeta, freeciv, atlantik (and more to follow)
	  - read DESIGN on how it works
	  - note: static HTML pages like freeciv's do currently not work 
	  because
	    KIO::NetAccess doesn't work inside another kio slave... have to 
	  figure out
	    how
	  - the following, found in kdelibs/kio/netaccess.h, says it all:
	  // If a troll sees this, he kills me


