2001-11-10 20:08:51  Rev 2721   dr_maux

	* kio_ggz/Makefile.am kio_ggz/kio_ggz.cpp kio_ggz/kio_ggz.h:
	  - no fake anymore: do real login
	  - display rooms as directories and MOTD as text file
	  - running ggz://localhost/ lists the contents
	  - running ggz://localhost/MOTD loads the motd in your favorite 
	  editor. This may
	    be HTML later (with colors etc...)
	  - well, you can now use Konqueror to conquer GGZ servers :-)


