	  files in KDE are
	    destroyed.
	    This is either an extraterrestric phenomenon or a bug in KDE's 
	  build system
	    which is currently resolved on kde-devel.
	    But, wait, maybe it's really the borg who are taking over some 
	  files in the
	    CVS.
	    "You are an io slave, we must assimilate you!"
	    "Noooooo please, I don't have prerelease quality yet!"
	    "Shit."


